WEBVTT

00:14:59.840 --> 00:15:03.656
I mean, you don't have to tell somebody
that their bald spot is growing

00:15:03.680 --> 00:15:05.296
or their baby's ugly.

00:15:05.320 --> 00:15:07.416
So, I'm just talking about --

00:15:07.440 --> 00:15:08.656
(Laughter)

00:15:08.680 --> 00:15:10.856
talking about the important things.

00:15:10.880 --> 00:15:12.096
So --

00:15:12.120 --> 00:15:15.320
(Laughter)

00:15:16.600 --> 00:15:18.016
So when you leave this room,

00:15:18.040 --> 00:15:22.480
I'd like you to observe yourself
in conversations with others.

00:15:23.360 --> 00:15:27.040
Imagine if you knew
what they were really thinking,

00:15:27.760 --> 00:15:30.360
and imagine if you knew
what they were really like ...